A lot of you are coming
from Mac OS 9 to Mac OS X.

00:35:49.030 --> 00:35:50.620
You're carbonizing your products.

00:35:50.670 --> 00:35:52.420
And here's a product that's
shipping on 10 today.

00:35:52.760 --> 00:35:55.810
They've got it inside
of a Mac OS X window.

