But the contents of the window
are completely platinum.

00:35:59.600 --> 00:36:01.940
The disclosure triangle on
the folder is the platinum,

00:36:01.940 --> 00:36:02.870
the Mac OS 9 appearance.

00:36:03.010 --> 00:36:04.990
The folders themselves,
Mac OS 9 appearance.

00:36:05.140 --> 00:36:09.430
The list background is gray and white,
Mac OS 9 background.

00:36:09.550 --> 00:36:12.910
So what this leads me to
believe as a user is that,

00:36:13.010 --> 00:36:14.860
well, is this a native Mac OS X app?

