Or I'm not sure,
because it feels like kind of 9.

00:36:19.620 --> 00:36:22.180
Make sure that every interface
element that you draw is native for

00:36:22.190 --> 00:36:24.390
the platform on which you're on.

00:36:24.460 --> 00:36:26.570
What's your citizenship?

