Tabs, you know,
and some of this is because Apple in

00:36:57.560 --> 00:36:59.700
the past didn't have a tab control.

00:36:59.850 --> 00:37:03.730
So developers had to come up with
another way of allowing users to

00:37:03.730 --> 00:37:05.880
switch the pane in a dialog box.

