but in context,

00:37:19.240 --> 00:37:21.790
you would have no idea that they
switched the pane of the window.

00:37:21.800 --> 00:37:24.640
They just look like two buttons that
happen to be really close together.

00:37:24.640 --> 00:37:29.000
So if you've got a tabbed interface,
use the standard Mac OS X tabs,

00:37:29.000 --> 00:37:30.580
which look like this.

00:37:30.680 --> 00:37:33.840
They're available north, south, east,
