And yet it's very hard
to navigate this panel.

00:41:41.570 --> 00:41:46.930
It's very hard to tell what's
here and you have to actually

00:41:46.930 --> 00:41:46.930
read every single element

00:41:47.280 --> 00:41:49.960
and think about it in its context
relative to the other elements to think

00:41:49.990 --> 00:41:52.150
about whether it's the one that you want.

00:41:52.150 --> 00:41:54.000
The alternative is of course
to apply the interface guide,

00:41:54.000 --> 00:41:56.700
the layout guidelines and
you get something like this,

