which has grouping of
elements that are related,

00:42:00.580 --> 00:42:03.990
it uses a separator bar,
it uses white space,

00:42:03.990 --> 00:42:08.890
and suddenly now you can quickly
scan the categories and zero in on

00:42:08.940 --> 00:42:12.410
the category that you're interested
of the setting that you're after,

00:42:12.410 --> 00:42:12.410
right?

