00:45:12.980 --> 00:45:17.860
We've got overuse of group boxes, which,
you know, aren't even laid out nicely,

00:45:17.970 --> 00:45:20.890
so I don't know what's grouped
together really and why.

00:45:20.900 --> 00:45:21.860
There's no labels.

00:45:21.920 --> 00:45:27.520
We've got interface elements like a
