00:46:08.690 --> 00:46:11.700
So here's an example where someone
had a creative idea and yet when they,

00:46:11.700 --> 00:46:13.420
if they had done usability
testing or whatever,

00:46:13.420 --> 00:46:15.290
they would have realized
