01:00:13.650 --> 01:00:15.670
As we look at products
coming to Mac OS X,

01:00:15.780 --> 01:00:18.810
and this is true on Mac OS 9,
but particularly on Mac OS X as

01:00:19.040 --> 01:00:22.300
