other functionality that we're going to

01:02:55.150 --> 01:02:59.300
talk about in one of the sessions here,
114, app packaging and document binding.

01:02:59.300 --> 01:03:02.280
And in other sessions you're going
to hear a lot about the bundle,

01:03:02.280 --> 01:03:03.660
the application bundle.

01:03:03.660 --> 01:03:05.060
So consistency everywhere.

01:03:05.120 --> 01:03:07.890
